discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/9/b918990a6a25d5b7d698f388f6401ce59a7eb81b.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-06-11 142757\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/9/b918990a6a25d5b7d698f388f6401ce59a7eb81b.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-06-11 142757\" width=\"362\" height=\"320\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-06-11 142757</span><span class=\"informations\">362×320 13.3 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\nI expect to see a percentage of 40%<br />\n8 hours + 8 hours = 16 hours per week<br />\ntotal capacity 40<br />\n16/40 = 40%<br />\nWhy Monday shows me 2%<br />\nand 0.37 Hours on 40 Hours (capacity per week)?<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/0/00b8d8fbbe4ed7f1c04f19fc7617d999ba56714e.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-06-11 142939\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/0/00b8d8fbbe4ed7f1c04f19fc7617d999ba56714e.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-06-11 142939\" width=\"591\" height=\"277\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-06-11 142939</span><span class=\"informations\">591×277 16.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>thank you<br />\nFederico</p>"
